 40	/*all the TARMA stuff:
 41	  this is based on the modelling framework provided in
 42	  "M. Laner, P. Svoboda and M. Rupp, Modeling Randomness in Network Traffic, SIGMETRICS/Performance'12, London, UK, 2012".
 43	
